      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with this beauty, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or fun weekend road trips. It runs great and looks even better in person! I\u2019m super excited to find it a new home where it\u2019ll be appreciated just as much as I\u2019ve enjoyed it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and tell you more about it!",
