    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized torque across the rev range. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity, including a documented subframe reinforcement and cooling system refresh. Suspension bushings remain compliant yet firm, providing the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance characteristic of this M-division icon. A well-sorted driver's example for those who prioritize mechanical synchronization and throttle response over cosmetic perfection.",
