      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor road peppering on the front bumper consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and features supple leather upholstery that shows minimal bolster wear. All electronic components, including the dual-zone climate control and premium infotainment system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust; it shifts smoothly through all gears and the engine pull is consistent and strong. We have recently performed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection to ensure it is road-ready. While there are a few light surface scratches near the trunk loading area, the overall presentation is professional and clean. It represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability for the discerning buyer.",
